title: Four Seasons Natural Foods Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Buffet, Salad bar, Take-out
description: Veggie cafe associated with the health food store by the same name though the store portion moved out into its own space in 2015. Offers an all-vegan buffet and loads of vegan desserts and smoothies/shakes options for which you can choose your milk base. Many vegan snacks / to-go items.
